# Desktop Performance Optimization Plan

## Goal Description
Address user-reported lag on the desktop version. The lag is primarily caused by:
1.  **Expensive Animations**: Large `blur` filters and gradients animating indefinitely in [AnimatedBackground](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/Shop.tsx#29-71).
2.  **Excessive Re-renders**: The [Hero](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/Landing.tsx#182-496) section's simulation loop (updating every 1.2s) triggers re-renders of the entire Hero component.
3.  **Dead Network Requests**: A non-existent `index.css` is being requested.

## User Review Required
> [!TIP]
> This optimization reorganizes the code to be more efficient. No visual features will be removed, but the code structure will change slightly to isolate heavy components.

## Proposed Changes

### Components Layer
#### [NEW] [components/AnimatedBackground.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/components/AnimatedBackground.tsx)
- Extract the background logic from [Landing.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/Landing.tsx).
- **Optimization**: Add `will-change: transform` to hint the browser to promote layers to GPU.
- **Optimization**: Use `React.memo` to prevent re-renders when parent state changes.

#### [NEW] [components/HeroTerminal.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/components/HeroTerminal.tsx)
- Extract the "Terminal/Dashboard" mockup from [Landing.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/Landing.tsx).
- Move the `setInterval` simulation logic *inside* this component.
- **Benefit**: State updates in the terminal will only re-render the terminal, not the Main Title, Buttons, or Background.

### Pages layer
