- Replace inline background with `<AnimatedBackground />`.
- Replace inline terminal with `<HeroTerminal />`.
- Remove the simulation state from the main component.

#### [MODIFY] [Shop.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/Shop.tsx)
- Replace inline background with `<AnimatedBackground />`.

### Root
#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/index.html)
